{"id": "1311256136090914816", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "其實彌利根本不知道那東西是不是圖魯，只是那東西出現在圖魯的屍骨前面於是她深信那就是圖魯（或是她的神）\n但從結果來看那就不是個好東西（", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T09:03:44.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
