{"id": "1311316518612504626", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~什麼反推~~\n好啦其實整個神國就是一個代代相傳的謊言\n每代神王都沒敢披露 真有默契", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T13:03:41.120000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
