{"id": "1311321199392985118", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "沒有喔\n圖魯是在米粒當上副主教才登基的\n米粒年紀比圖魯大", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T13:22:17.105000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1311321700549263380", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且利莫里亞的神王傳位是用海選小孩的方式 不是王室傳承", "timestamp": "2024-11-27T13:24:16.590000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
